OL,3,CJeff Bezos 'in talks to join
OL,4,Cconsortium eyeing Liverpool stake'
OL,6,FAmazon founder Jeff Bezos has held
OL,7,Ftalks over potentially joining a
OL,8,Fconsortium which has expressed an
OL,9,Finterest in buying a minority stake in
OL,10,FLiverpool, according to reports.
OL,12,FIt is understood that Bezos, one of
OL,13,Fthe world's richest men, could become
OL,14,Fpart of a syndicate which is led by
OL,15,FAmit Bhatia, the son-in-law of
OL,16,Fbillionaire steel tycoon Lakshmi
OL,17,FMittal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
