OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784751304
OL,3,CJeff Bezos 'in talks to join
OL,4,Cconsortium eyeing Liverpool stake'
OL,6,FOn Tuesday 21 July, Liverpool owners
OL,7,FFenway Sports Group confirmed that
OL,8,FBhatia's group had approached them to
OL,9,Fdiscuss investing in the club.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for FSG said: "An
OL,12,Finvestment consortium led, managed,
OL,13,Fand represented by Amit Bhatia has
OL,14,Fexpressed interest in making a
OL,15,Fstrategic minority investment in
OL,16,FLiverpool Football Club."
OL,26,@sD@^OUxD@YO]
