OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784751304
OL,3,CJeff Bezos 'in talks to join
OL,4,Cconsortium eyeing Liverpool stake'
OL,6,FBezos, who has a fortune worth an
OL,7,Festimated #192billion according to
OL,8,FForbes, has reportedly explored
OL,9,Fprevious bids for the NFL's Seattle
OL,10,FSeahawks and Washington Commanders,
OL,11,Fbut decided against pursuing either
OL,12,Fdeal.
OL,14,FNews of Bhatia's interest in Liverpool
OL,15,Fcame on the same day that the 46-year-
OL,16,Fold stepped down from the board at QPR
OL,17,Fto end an 18-year association with the
OL,18,FChampionship club, transferring his
OL,19,Fstake to majority owner Ruben
OL,20,FGnanalingam.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
