OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784751304
OL,3,CJeff Bezos 'in talks to join
OL,4,Cconsortium eyeing Liverpool stake'
OL,6,FIn 2023, FSG sold a minority stake in
OL,7,FLiverpool to investment firm Dynasty
OL,8,Fand any deal with Bhatia, should it
OL,9,Fproceed, is expected to be along
OL,10,Fsimilar lines.
OL,12,FFSG, which also owns the Boston Red
OL,13,FSox and the Pittsburgh Penguins,
OL,14,Fbought Liverpool in 2010 for
OL,15,F#300million. Forbes recently valued
OL,16,Fthe club at #4.6billion.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
